        "translation": "He replied, \"There's no difference between giving money and giving the Dharma equally.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c05_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行者曰甚麼道爭消得贄嚫。",
        "translation": "The practitioner said, \"What path is there to pursue in order to obtain the dakṣiṇā?",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c06_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "便將出去。",
        "translation": "He then went out.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c06_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須臾復入曰請施財。",
        "translation": "He entered again a moment later and said, \"Please give money.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c06_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "黃蘗曰。",
        "translation": "Huang Chang said.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c07_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "財法二施等無差別。",
        "translation": "'There's no difference between giving money and giving the Dharma.'",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c07_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃嚫。",
        "translation": "He then gave dakṣiṇā.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c07_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行者甞接待往來。",
        "translation": "The practitioner used to receive people who came and went.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c07_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有僧問曰行者接待不易。",
