        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此去三十年後。",
        "translation": "\"Thirty years have passed since then.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c16_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須知一回飲水一回咽。",
        "translation": "'You must know that once you drink water, you'll swallow it again.'",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c16_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其女子聞之亦悟曰。",
