        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰知盡大地人性命被奯上座劄將去也(五燈會元．先覺宗乘)。",
        "translation": "\"Who would have known that the whole world's human life would be snapped away by the Śākyamuni?\" (Wu Dōshō Huiyuan: Xianjue Zongsheng).",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c17_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "張秀才名拙。",
