        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "覓巧尚不可得。",
        "translation": "\"We can't find any ingenuity yet.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c20_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拙自何來。",
        "translation": "Where did clumsiness come from?",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c20_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "張忽有省。",
