        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "光明寂照徧河沙。",
        "translation": "\"Luminous quiescence and illumination pervade the sands of the river.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c21_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "凡聖含靈共我家。",
        "translation": "Ordinary people and sages contain spirits that share my home.",
