        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一念不生全體現。",
        "translation": "A single thought that isn't produced is all that appears.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c21_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六根纔動被雲遮。",
        "translation": "The six faculties are unmoving and obscured by clouds.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c22_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "斷除煩惱重增病。",
        "translation": "Their afflictions are eliminated, and they become seriously ill.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c22_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "趨向真如亦是邪。",
        "translation": "It's also wrong to tend toward the true nature.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c22_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨順世緣無罣礙。",
        "translation": "He follows worldly conditions without obstruction.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0215c23_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "涅槃生死等空華(五燈會元)。",
