        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "予閱傳燈諸錄。",
        "translation": "I read the records of the Transmission of the Lamp.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0216a01_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "錄諸子問答機緣如此。",
        "translation": "This is how I recorded the sons' questions and answers about their abilities.",
        "source": "X88n1646_018:0216a01_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其他行事不得而詳也。",
